.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7830bd42a802230b87f56b9a730158a2bc3982e4","tid":2392832,"uid":375135,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bc8ea16c8d2b094ff59e609fb856c809e7060549","tid":2392832,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T05:08:13.000Z","msg":"財經事務及庫務局局長許正宇批評，美國對本港提出的所謂制裁手法拙劣、行徑荒誕，重申單方面制裁不符合國際法，在本港沒有法律效力，亦不會對本港機構構成本地法律責任，表明特區政府絕對不受恫嚇。<br />\n<br />\n民建聯議員黃定光在立法會會議上關注，特區政府會否要求美國撤銷制裁。另一名民建聯議員葛珮帆就建議，特區政府提出反制措施。建制派議員何君堯就要求政府交代，受美方制裁的政府官員，目前使用銀行戶口的情況。<br />\n<br />\n許正宇表示，不評論官員個別情況，指監管機構曾與金融機構溝通，希望他們考慮風險的同時，平衡對客戶的影響。他指，所謂制裁暴露美方的虛偽，不會對本港國際金融及貿易中心地位有影響，亦表示《香港國安法》實施以來，本港金融市場有序運作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1573838-20210203.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1573838-20210203.htm&d=FM8PVMPbIH5fyb1BVmxPrRjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=a65ebf6c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1573838-20210203.htm&h=ce6b79eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1573838-20210203.htm</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T06:13:57.000Z","msg":"邊位，聽都未聽過有個咁既人。 歡迎制裁"},{"pid":"0ad2a4d87db657c534301b9f9d7948c81394725f","tid":2392832,"uid":54800,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2d3ef09823481f3636a02e3f051260ae236a840a","tid":2392832,"uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T05:33:25.000Z","msg":"原來有個局長叫許正宇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T06:24:31.000Z","msg":"Financial Services and the Treasury<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n許正宇響一個有錢嘅左派屋企出世，阿爸許宏全1968年喺廈門大學化學系畢業，係一名老師，亦都係文革先鋒，喺左派社團入面好有名氣。響1970至74年間喺福建寧德市工業局做中共幹部，曾經被人懷疑係中共黨員。1974年許宏全放棄咗做中共幹部，去咗香港做生果檔小販。不過《壹週刊》喺2008年訪問過佢五伯許宏點，佢話當年許宏全係「共產黨派佢落嚟香港搞文革、搞政治，佢做小販純粹係為咗生存同掩飾」[4]。後嚟許正宇轉到貿易公司做嘢，仲先後到廣州同福建設廠......<br />\n<br />\n呢檔維基邊個起架~??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://zh-yue.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%A8%B1%E6%AD%A3%E5%AE%87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh-yue.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E8%25A8%25B1%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E5%25AE%2587&d=FM8PVMPbIH5fyb1BVmxPrRjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=155cd04f\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh-yue.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%A8%B1%E6%AD%A3%E5%AE%87</a>"},{"pid":"832bdab29858bce8c339785352cd993fddcbdebe","tid":2392832,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ad2a4d87db657c534301b9f9d7948c81394725f","tid":2392832,"uid":54800,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2d3ef09823481f3636a02e3f051260ae236a840a","tid":2392832,"uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T05:33:25.000Z","msg":"原來有個局長叫許正宇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T06:24:31.000Z","msg":"Financial Services and the Treasury<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n許正宇響一個有錢嘅左派屋企出世，阿爸許宏全1968年喺廈門大學化學系畢業，係一名老師，亦都係文革先鋒，喺左派社團入面好有名氣。響1970至74年間喺福建寧德市工業局做中共幹部，曾經被人懷疑係中共黨員。1974年許宏全放棄咗做中共幹部，去咗香港做生果檔小販。不過《壹週刊》喺2008年訪問過佢五伯許宏點，佢話當年許宏全係「共產黨派佢落嚟香港搞文革、搞政治，佢做小販純粹係為咗生存同掩飾」[4]。後嚟許正宇轉到貿易公司做嘢，仲先後到廣州同福建設廠......<br />\n<br />\n呢檔維基邊個起架~??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://zh-yue.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%A8%B1%E6%AD%A3%E5%AE%87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh-yue.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E8%25A8%25B1%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E5%25AE%2587&d=FM8PVMPbIH5fyb1BVmxPrRjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=155cd04f\" t